<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <title>응급실 검색</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,minimum-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=no" />
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/common.css" />
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>
<body>
<div id="wrapper" class="main">
    <div class="section">
        <header>

            <div class="main-ti">
                <h1>가까운 응급실 검색 <br/>병원 통합 검색</h1>
                <p>주소를 입력해주세요. 주소와 가장 가까운 10km 이내 응급실을 알려드립니다.</p>
            </div>

        </header>
        <div id="contents">
            <div class="search_main">
                <form name="topSearchForm" id="topSearchForm" action="/search" method = "post">
                    <fieldset>
                        <legend>통합 검색</legend>
                        <div class="search_area">
                            <input type="text" class="form-control inptxt" id="address_kakao" name="address">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn_search" id="btn-save"><span class="hide">검색</span></button>
                        </div>

                    </fieldset>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
    <div id="bg">
    </div>
</div>

<script src="//t1.daumcdn.net/mapjsapi/bundle/postcode/prod/postcode.v2.js"></script>
<script>
        window.onload = function() {
            document.getElementById("address_kakao").addEventListener("click", function(){

                new daum.Postcode({
                    oncomplete: function(data) {
                        document.getElementById("address_kakao").value = data.address;
                    }
                }).open();
            });
        }
</script>

</body>
</html>